@piquark6046 

01. Since the Blind app does not use a separate ad server, does that mean ad blocking is not possible and I have to use it without ad block?
(I am not an expert, so I cannot understand why ad blocking is impossible because it does not use a separate server. Anyway, since Adguard is an 'ad blocking' program, I think there should be a solution for this.)

